strations]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tesla is reportedly building a compact crossover codenamed 'Redwood']]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>据<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-plans-build-new-electric-vehicles-mid-2025-sources-2024-01-24/"><em>知情人士</em></a>透露，特斯拉正在研发代号为“Redwood”的紧凑型跨界电动汽车，预计将于 2025 年 6 月开始生产。据报道，该公司去年向供应商发出了新车型的报价请求，预计每周产量为 10,000 辆。</p><p>这一传言与埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 在 2023 年 5 月股东大会上的<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/05/16/elon-musk-teases-two-new-evs-says-tesla-is-already-building-one/">言论</a>相符，即特斯拉正在开发两款新的电动汽车车型，年销量合计可达 500 万辆。他当时表示：“产品的设计和制造技术都远远领先于行业中的其他产品。”</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2018-08-18-elon-musk-talks-25k-tesla.html">一段时间</a>以来，特斯拉也一直承诺推出售价 25,000 美元的汽车，但马斯克放弃了这一想法，但由于消费者利率较高（最便宜的 Model 3 售价为 38,990 美元） <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.pcmag.com/news/elon-musk-tesla-is-obviously-still-working-on-a-25000-ev">，又重新启动了该</a>计划。不过，<em>路透社</em>的消息人士并未提及该车将于 2025 年上市的价格。</p><p>对特斯拉来说，这份报告发布的时机恰逢其时，因为批评者最近一直<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-03/how-will-tesla-overcome-a-stale-lineup-in-2024-transcript">在批评该公司</a>在相对陈旧的 Model 3 和 Y 设计上坐以待毙。在定于今天下午（1 月 24 日）举行的特斯拉财报电话会议上，推出新电动汽车的时机是投资者投票最多的问题之一。</p><p>如果新车符合马斯克的描述，它们可以帮助减轻这些担忧。与此同时，特斯拉开始推出其<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/teslas-cybertruck-is-a-dystopian-masturbatory-fantasy-225648188.html">Cyber​​truck 电动汽车</a>，但其评价褒贬不一，一些用户谴责<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://electrek.co/2023/10/24/internet-arguing-tesla-cybertrucks-build-quality/">质量问题</a>，另一些用户则<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.carscoops.com/2023/12/first-tesla-cybertruck-reviews-are-in-heres-what-theyre-saying/">称赞</a>该车的性能和大胆。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/tesla-is-reportedly-building-a-compact-crossover-codenamed-redwood-103223757.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/tesla-is-reportedly-building-a-compact-crossover-codenamed-redwood-103223757.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> dd3b201d-6b93-4b0a-9c8a-1d870aec2ac9 </guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Steve Dent]]></dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder><![CDATA[Engadget]]></dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Wed, 24 Jan 2024 10:32:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1706092345</ingested><modified> 2024-01-24T10:32:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2F6eb71c70-ba9d-11ee-bffe-c3c9b25abc27&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=9d0021dcd1a343022ca7ec827f52f5ab4df4e100" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-01%2F6eb71c70-ba9d-11ee-bffe-c3c9b25abc27&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=b58204b22e0a2eb4f47a44d47e218fc53022db40" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![C